{"tid":2507774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【立法會通過修訂入境條例】","createTime":"2021-04-28T08:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T09:38:38.000Z","uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4c070b015c4c877fea7ea867267c6af546c6f02f","tid":2507774,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"【立法會通過修訂入境條例】<br />\n<br />\n立法會以39票贊成、2票反對，三讀通過《2020年入境（修訂）條例草案》，將於8月1日生效。修例被指是「鎖港」，當中訂明保安局局長可賦權入境處處長，指示任何運輸工具不可運載某乘客或某乘組人員，疑限制港人出入境自由。保安局局長李家超在會上重申，修訂是為了執行特區《國際民用航空公約》的要求，對港人的出入境自由沒有任何影響。<br />\n<br />\nTG<br />\n獨立媒體"},{"pid":"eebc25bbe4b48bd60c2130f311d98af908212811","tid":2507774,"uid":7824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"算啦 香港無得救㗎啦 自求多福啦"},{"pid":"e3baa15db6db3af2f58544da9e9085502095efa7","tid":2507774,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbvHquWURirAjDJ2EdRPWa8iX6XHLoGZTWN9cYbsNdtg2?filename=eTX9pMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTX9pMA.jpg&h=c100f2ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7ec6bd4b12e04d6ea1dfb0bc318f0fa1c396343","tid":2507774,"uid":342855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eebc25bbe4b48bd60c2130f311d98af908212811","tid":2507774,"uid":7824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"算啦 香港無得救㗎啦 自求多福啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"你偷影人哋更加無得救"},{"pid":"0826ada14eca7cb19afb77d7c4c4c4db905af6b6","tid":2507774,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"又有國際核陣比外國 睇黎支共急了急了 我地又贏lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd51964c751564459792ac477339f38e8482d31","tid":2507774,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eebc25bbe4b48bd60c2130f311d98af908212811","tid":2507774,"uid":7824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"sc