須有拘捕同即刻槍斃"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9983565a8636d5f22ba4ccd172fefa5f4e2c726","tid":2507774,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c070b015c4c877fea7ea867267c6af546c6f02f","tid":2507774,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"【立法會通過修訂入境條例】<br />\n<br />\n立法會以39票贊成、2票反對，三讀通過《2020年入境（修訂）條例草案》，將於8月1日生效。修例被指是「鎖港」，當中訂明保安局局長可賦權入境處處長，指示任何運輸工具不可運載某乘客或某乘組人員，疑限制港人出入境自由。保安局局長李家超在會上重申，修訂是為了執行特區《國際民用航空公約》的要求，對港人的出入境自由沒有任何影響。<br />\n<br />\nTG<br />\n獨立媒體"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:34:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=a0370667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n按立法會會議 》最新投票結果<br />\n<br />\n40票讚成，2票反對，二讀通過。<br />\n39票讚成，2票反對，三讀通過。"},{"pid":"8ea61fc80016bcee5701e93027056b00c3b4168a","tid":2507774,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b99f94141c96699d9434e0fe25116b4e60702c","tid":2507774,"uid":248578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ca67cb9ab98ef74f576220348acbe92e428a009","tid":2507774,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10a1d3147fde6f393f42d57c94c3882e1b1c754e","tid":2507774,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"見你一入到機場<br />\n實知道你移民走佬<br />\n即刻莫須有拘捕同即刻槍斃"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09: